NOTE on third-party content:

This project is a template/orchestrator that helps users compose MES/MOM
specification documents based on the ENAA "MES/MOM 導入のための標準業務一覧"
(G25-029 series, 2025-09-01 official version), published by 一般財団法人
エンジニアリング協会 (Engineering Advancement Association of Japan, ENAA).

ENAA materials are NOT bundled with this project. Users are required to
download them directly from the official ENAA site:
  https://www.enaa.or.jp/research/smart/mes

ENAA materials are subject to ENAA's own license terms (in-house and RFP
secondary use permitted, with mandatory attribution). The MIT License above
applies only to the source code and documentation in this repository, NOT
to ENAA materials.

When using outputs generated by this template, the ENAA attribution text
(automatically inserted by the template) MUST be retained per ENAA's
licensing terms.
